---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import PageHero from '../components/PageHero.astro';
import CtaBand from '../components/CtaBand.astro';
import { founder } from '../data/content';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Our Story"
  description="Why The Freedom School exists — and the belief that every young person deserves an education that helps them think for themselves."
>
  <PageHero
    eyebrow="Our Story"
    title="Why The Freedom School exists"
    lead="It began with a simple, stubborn belief: that every young person deserves an education that helps them think for themselves."
    coral={1}
  />

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container container--narrow flow story">
      <p>
        Most schools were built for a different century. They reward memorizing over thinking, ranking over
        growth, and quiet compliance over real curiosity. Teenagers spend years learning things they’ll never
        use — and slowly lose touch with what makes them <em>them</em>.
      </p>
      <p>
        We’re building something different. The Freedom School is a fully online high school where teens learn
        <strong>how to think, not what to think</strong>. We trade stress and conformity for curiosity and
        purpose, and we help young people free their minds from manipulation, conditioning and fear — so they
        can see the world clearly and shape it as it could be.
      </p>

      <p>
        But we refuse the usual trade-off. Traditional schools choose structure and crush curiosity. Many
        alternative schools choose freedom and quietly leave gaps that close doors later. We protect a small,
        essential foundation — reading and writing well, real-world numeracy, clear thinking, the ability to
        learn anything, and understanding how money and the world work — and above it, your child is free. The
        foundation isn’t the cage around freedom; it’s the launchpad beneath it.
      </p>

      <blockquote class="pull">
        We’re here to awaken the next generation of free thinkers, creators and visionaries.
      </blockquote>

      <p>
        Every week, our students create something of their own — turning ideas into action and imagination into
        reality. That’s the magic we’re making on Earth: a generation who know how to think critically, live
        consciously, and lead with compassion.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section--cream">
    <div class="container founder-grid">
      <div class="founder-portrait">
        <span class="founder-monogram" aria-hidden="true">{founder.name.charAt(0)}</span>
        <img src={founder.aboutImage} alt={`${founder.name}, Founder of The Freedom School`} loading="lazy" onerror="this.remove()" />
      </div>
      <div class="founder-bio flow">
        <p class="eyebrow">Meet the founder</p>
        <h2>Hi, I’m {founder.name}</h2>
        {founder.bio.map((para) => <p>{para}</p>)}
        <p class="founder-sign">
          <strong>{founder.name}</strong> · {founder.role}<br />
          <span class="founder-cred">{founder.credential}</span>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <CtaBand title="Ready to be part of the movement?" coral={3} />
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .story p { font-size: 1.15rem; line-height: 1.7; color: var(--text); }
  .story em { color: var(--coral-ink); font-style: italic; }
  .pull {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-weight: 500;
    font-size: clamp(1.4rem, 1rem + 1.8vw, 2rem);
    line-height: 1.3;
    color: var(--ink);
    border-left: 4px solid var(--coral);
    padding-left: 1.25rem;
    margin-block: 0.5rem;
    text-wrap: balance;
  }
  .founder-grid { display: grid; gap: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem); align-items: start; }
  @media (min-width: 860px) { .founder-grid { grid-template-columns: 0.85fr 1.15fr; } }

  .founder-portrait {
    position: relative;
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 360px;
    aspect-ratio: 4 / 5;
    border-radius: var(--r-lg);
    overflow: hidden;
    justify-self: center;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow);
  }
  @media (min-width: 860px) { .founder-portrait { position: sticky; top: 6rem; } }
  .founder-monogram {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    background: linear-gradient(150deg, var(--coral) 0%, var(--coral-strong) 100%);
    color: #fff;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: clamp(5rem, 18vw, 8rem);
  }
  .founder-portrait img {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    object-position: center 15%;
  }

  .founder-bio h2 { font-size: clamp(1.7rem, 1.2rem + 2vw, 2.4rem); }
  .founder-bio p { color: var(--text); line-height: 1.7; }
  .founder-sign { margin-top: 1.5rem; color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.5; }
  .founder-sign strong { color: var(--ink); font-family: var(--font-display); }
  .founder-cred { color: var(--coral-ink); font-size: var(--fs-sm); }
</style>
